title: Lakers-Clippers, Dak Prescott, Baker Mayfield, & NCAAFB rankings

description:
Colin explains why Kawhi Leonard chose the Clippers over the Lakers, why he likes Dak Prescott, the weakness of Baker Mayfield, and his thoughts on the NCAAFB rankings. Guests include Nick Wright, Joel Klatt, Kareem Jackson, and Chris Broussard.
